      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by. You know, I\u2019ve had a lot of cars over the years, but this one is truly special\u2014it\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy. It\u2019s in such incredible shape that it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it from day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure every inch stays spotless. There might be a tiny, almost invisible mark if you look with a magnifying glass, but honestly, she\u2019s as close to perfect as they come. I\u2019m looking for someone who will love it as much as I do. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
